---
// AboutPrytulaFoundation.astro
---

<section class="yellow-section">
  <div class="three-column-container">
    <div class="column">
      <h3 class="column-title">ABOUT SERHIY PRYTULA</h3>
      <p class="text-block">
        Serhiy Prytula is a Ukrainian volunteer and founder of the Serhiy Prytula Charity Foundation,
        as well as a former leading host of one of Ukraine's most popular TV shows. Since 2014, he has
        been actively involved in humanitarian initiatives, and after Russia's full-scale invasion in 2022,
        he expanded his efforts with a team of over 100 people to provide aid to both the military and civilians.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="column">
      <h3 class="column-title">ABOUT UKRAINIAN HUB</h3>
      <img src="/images/ukrainianhub-logo.svg" alt="Ukrainian Hub" class="ukrainian-hub-logo" />
      <p class="text-block">
        Ukrainian Hub is an international non-profit organization with offices in Ukraine, Portugal,
        and the United States. We empower Ukrainian entrepreneurs and displaced professionals through
        business education, mentoring, and global networking. Our mission is to support the Ukrainian
        community worldwide and foster innovation and entrepreneurship.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="column">
      <h3 class="column-title">ONE BILLION FUNDRAISER</h3>
      <p class="text-block">
        Together, we can prevent mass russian strikes on Ukrainian cities. Our One Billion campaign aims
        to raise critical funds for advanced air defense systems, drones, and military equipment that will
        protect Ukrainian civilians and critical infrastructure from ongoing attacks.
      </p>
      <p class="text-block">
        Every contribution brings us closer to securing the safety of millions of Ukrainians. The funds
        raised will be allocated to the most urgent defense needs, identified in collaboration with
        Ukrainian military leadership and defense experts.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .yellow-section {
    background: var(--bg-yellow);
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
    color: var(--text-black);
  }

  .three-column-container {
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--paragraph-gap);
  }

  .column-title {
    font-size: var(--text-section-md);
    font-weight: var(--font-black);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-section-md);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .ukrainian-hub-logo {
    width: 120px;
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .text-block {
    font-size: var(--text-body-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-body);
  }

  .text-block + .text-block {
    margin-top: var(--paragraph-gap);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .three-column-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .yellow-section {
      padding: var(--section-padding-y-mobile) var(--section-padding-x);
    }
  }
</style>
